# 4. Functional Requirements

## 4.1 Authentication Module

Features:

* Login using email and password
* Select role during login
* Forgot password functionality
* JWT-based authentication
* Role-based authorization

---

## 4.2 Student Module

Students can:

* View assignments by subject.
* Submit assignments.
* Resubmit assignments.
* Submit assignments after deadline with warning.
* Provide reason for late submission.
* View submission status.
* View faculty feedback.
* Participate in team assignments.
* Receive email notifications.
* Chat with faculty.

---

## 4.3 Faculty Module

Faculty can:

* Create assignments.
* Specify:

  * File format restrictions
  * Team or individual submissions
  * Deadline
  * Subject
  * Branch and section
* Approve submissions.
* Reject submissions with reasons.
* Reapprove rejected submissions.
* View late submissions separately.
* Bulk approve and reject submissions.
* Export reports.
* View pending counts.

---

## 4.4 Team Management Module

Features:

* Team creation.
* Team invitation.
* Team member management.
* Team leader selection.
* Only team leader can submit.
* Team submission tracking.

---

## 4.5 Assignment Module

Assignment details:

* Title
* Description
* Subject
* Branch
* Section
* Deadline
* Allowed file types
* Submission type
* Maximum team size
* Attachments

---

## 4.6 Submission Module

Submission data:

* Submission timestamp
* Status
* Approval status
* Feedback
* Rejection reason
* Late submission reason
* File attachments

---

## 4.7 Chat Module

Features:

* Student and faculty messaging.
* Assignment-specific chat rooms.
* Submission-specific discussions.
* Comment sections.

---

## 4.8 Notification Module

Notifications for:

* Assignment creation
* Submission confirmation
* Approval
* Rejection
* Reapproval
* Team invitations

Notifications will be delivered through:

* In-app notifications
* Email notifications

---

## 4.9 File Preview Module

Supported formats:

* PDF
* DOC
* DOCX
* PPT
* PPTX
* XLS
* XLSX
* PNG
* JPG
* ZIP
* MP4

---

## 4.10 Syllabus Module

Features:

* Subject-wise syllabus display.
* Branch-wise syllabus display.
* Semester-wise syllabus display.
* Lab syllabus integration.
* Faculty assignment creation using syllabus selection.

---

## 4.11 Analytics Module

Faculty Dashboard:

* Total assignments
* Pending submissions
* Approved submissions
* Rejected submissions
* Late submissions

Admin Dashboard:

* Total users
* Branch-wise statistics
* Section-wise statistics
* Student activity
* Submission trends

---

## 4.12 Export Module

Supported exports:

* CSV
* Excel

Exported data includes:

* Student details
* Submission time
* Approval status
* Rejection reasons
* Faculty actions
* Activity logs

